rows.label: qst650101_msg0003
rows.name: Did they escape from the World Tree?

rows.label: qst650101_msg0005
rows.name:
There is no reason to let them
live. I will dispose of them.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0006
rows.name:
Whoa, hold on. Let's just
watch for a bit, T-elos Re:.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0008
rows.name:
The Driver of the Aegis and the
Flamebringer of Superbia!?

rows.label: qst650101_msg0009
rows.name:
To think you'd chase us
all the way here...

rows.label: qst650101_msg0010
rows.name:
We weren't chasing you. We
just happened to find you...

rows.label: qst650101_msg0011
rows.name:
Our plan is still in
its early stages...

rows.label: qst650101_msg0012
rows.name:
No, this is a once-in-a-lifetime
opportunity given to us
by Marveni-sama.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0013
rows.name: We'll defeat them here and now.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0015
rows.name:
Hmph. It was always
going to end like this.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0017
rows.name:
You foolish creatures...
This will be your grave.
